          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript is used for consultation and study and is a kind of manual and treatise on divination and reading the signs of planetary movement within the context of Hindu astrology and astronomy; makes predictions about the upcoming year related to agriculture and other aspects of human life. Two small astronomical tables of numbers appear near the end of the manuscript (f. 10r).</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
            <msItem>
              <title>Rājāvalī</title>
              <title type="vernacular">राजावली</title>
              <respStmt>
